
Necessary Software
------------------
- bpipe
- trimmomatic
- Oases and Velvet
- blat
- R (GenomicRanges,...) ? 
- bowtie2
- fastx tools
- samtools
- bash command-line tools - grep, awk,...

- also need human genome reference for extra filtering
this can be obtained from:
http://hgdownload.soe.ucsc.edu/goldenPath/hg19/bigZips/chromFa.tar.gz
untar and unzip then ... cat *.fa > hg19.fa

- Annotation...

